Package: tibbleOne
Type: Package
Title: Table One for 'Latex', 'Word', and 'Html' 'R Markdown' Documents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Byron", "Jaeger", email = "bcjaeger@uab.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7399-2299")),
    person("Boyi", "Guo", email = "boyiguo1@uab.edu", role = "ctb")
    )
Maintainer: Byron Jaeger <bcjaeger@uab.edu>
Description: In many academic papers, table 1 shows participant
    characteristics, often stratified by a categorical variable
    such as treatment group. There are many excellent packages
    available to compute the numbers in table 1. This package
    focuses on getting those numbers into a nice format that 
    works with 'R Markdown'.
